<TEXT>
   Ford Motor Co. announced cash rebates of
$1,000 on its large Ford LTD Crown Victoria and Mercury Grand
Marquis automobiles and $750 on its full-size Ford Bronco truck,
respectively.
   The rebates, announced Monday, continue indefinitely. The
vehicles were not included in an incentive package Ford announced
June 1 and is offering through July 31.
   Buyers of the luxury cars or Bronco do not have the option of
choosing low-interest financing instead of the rebates.
